OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,FThe design team chosen to create a
OL,7,Fmemorial to the victims of the
OL,8,FGrenfell Tower fire said they are
OL,9,Fhonoured to take up the task and that
OL,10,Fit is "a responsibility that we do not
OL,11,Ftake lightly".
OL,13,FLondon and Oxfordshire-based Freehaus
OL,14,Fdescribes itself as a firm which works
OL,15,F"with empathy".
