OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,FIt was chosen from a shortlist of five
OL,7,Fand will work with bereaved and
OL,8,Fsurvivor families as well as the local
OL,9,Fcommunity to produce a final design
OL,10,Fwhich is expected to be announced in
OL,11,Fmid-2027.
OL,13,FThe Grenfell Tower Memorial Commission
OL,14,Fhas been consulting on plans for a
OL,15,Fpermanent memorial in the area of the
OL,16,Ftower, with previously reported
OL,17,Frecommendations including a "sacred
OL,18,Fspace", designed to be a "peaceful
OL,19,Fplace for remembering and reflecting".
