OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,FThe commission's community
OL,7,Frepresentatives, said they feel
OL,8,F"confident that the right team has
OL,9,Fbeen selected to walk this road with
OL,10,Fus" and that they are now
OL,11,F"significantly closer to creating a
OL,12,Fbold, fitting and lasting memorial to
OL,13,Four 72 loved ones, and to our Grenfell
OL,14,Fcommunity, whose lives were forever
OL,15,Fchanged by the devastating tragedy" in
OL,16,FJune 2017.
