OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,FThe directors of Freehaus, Jonathan
OL,7,FHagos and Tom Bell, said they were
OL,8,F"honoured to have been chosen" and
OL,9,Fwill be "working closely with the
OL,10,Fbereaved, survivors, and the rest of
OL,11,Fthe Grenfell community, to design a
OL,12,Ffitting memorial for the many lives so
OL,13,Ftragically lost".
OL,15,FThey added: "As we take our first
OL,16,Fsteps in this journey, we want to
OL,17,Facknowledge the eight years of
OL,18,Fadvocacy and purposeful action led by
OL,19,Fthe Grenfell community that has
OL,20,Fbrought us here.
