OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,F"The design of this future memorial is
OL,7,Fa responsibility that we do not take
OL,8,Flightly."
OL,10,FThe firm was involved in the
OL,11,Frefurbishment of the Africa Centre
OL,12,Fheadquarters in Southwark and is
OL,13,Fcurrently designing a new civic hub in
OL,14,FWarwickshire and a series of
OL,15,Fexhibitions across London which chart
OL,16,Fthe experiences of marginalised people.
OL,18,FSeparately, the process to demolish
OL,19,FGrenfell tower began in September,
OL,20,Fwith the floor-by-floor deconstruction
OL,21,Fexpected to take two years.
