OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,FThe remains of the tower had stood in
OL,7,Fplace in the eight years since the
OL,8,Fdisaster, with a covering on the
OL,9,Fbuilding featuring a large green heart
OL,10,Faccompanied by the words "forever in
OL,11,Four hearts".
OL,13,FConfirmation earlier this year that
OL,14,Fthe tower was to be demolished was met
OL,15,Fwith criticism from some of the
OL,16,Fbereaved and survivors of the deadly
OL,17,Fblaze who expressed their upset and
OL,18,Fshock, saying they felt they had not
OL,19,Fhad their views considered before the
OL,20,Fdecision was taken.
OL,26,@rD@ZOUsD@KO]
