OL,3,CDesign team 'honoured' to be chosen to
OL,4,Ccreate Grenfell Tower memorial
OL,6,FSome of the bereaved and survivors had
OL,7,Fhoped it would stay in place until a
OL,8,Fpoint where charges were brought
OL,9,Fagainst those they deem responsible
OL,10,Ffor the fire.
OL,12,FPolice and prosecutors have previously
OL,13,Fsaid investigators would need until
OL,14,Fthe end of 2025 to complete their
OL,15,Finquiry, with final decisions on
OL,16,Fpotential criminal charges by the end
OL,17,Fof 2026.
OL,19,FThe near 10-year wait for justice has
OL,20,Fbeen described by families as
OL,21,F"unbearable".
